# LibertyCanvas Core

- Stack: Next.js 14 App Router, React 18, TypeScript strict, CSS Modules + Tailwind (`cn()` in `lib/utils/cn.ts`).
- AI: Vercel AI SDK via `lib/ai/provider.ts` (OpenAI → Anthropic → Groq fallback).
- Zero `any`. Prefer discriminated unions and Zod at API boundaries.
- No speculative imports or invented helpers. Reuse existing libs before adding npm packages.
- Functional state updates for fast UI: `setIndex((prev) => prev + 1)`, guard with `isTransitioning`.
- Keep server logic in RSC/route handlers; isolate streaming state in dedicated client hooks.
- Match existing naming, file layout, and a11y patterns (`role="group"` + `aria-label` on labeled divs).
- Active routes: `/`, `/assessment`, `/create`, `/diagnosis`, `/app/[id]`, `/quiz/[id]`.
- Run `npm run build` after non-trivial changes.
